cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.CR

Reasoning: The paper deals with computer vision and graph matching techniques to analyze egocentric and top-view videos. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of graph matching algorithms could also place the paper under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Finally, the use of drones and unmanned aerial vehicles could also place the paper under cs.RO (Robotics).
